    "The following field with a notable proportion of papers was Sports (7.7%) which may be attributable to the fact that exergames was a previously established category.",
    "Biosensors were used for objective monitoring of individual physical arousal, activity levels, and heart rate during exercise (e.g., Burin et al. 2020).",
